name: Anish Man Singh Shrestha
content: Hello Yup, that's me! Hello I am a biological machine using computational machines to learn about biological machines. I am an associate professor in the College of Computer Studies at De La Salle University Manila. I also lead the Bioinformatics Lab , Advanced Research Institute for Informatics, Computing, and Networking (AdRIC), DLSU Manila. Prior to this job, I was an assistant professor at the Department of Computational Biology and Medical Sciences, the University of Tokyo.
